1064	  char *any_one_container_log_dir = NULL;
{code}
Just the fact that a log dir was would is represented by this variable. I would replace it with a boolean (int). This will help to eliminate the extra logic on free().
{code}
1072	    if (create_directory_for_user(container_log_dir) != 0) {
